headline: Can Recent Moves Make DuPont a Stronger Opportunity for Investors in 2025?
summary: If you are wondering what to do with DuPont de Nemours stock right now, you are certainly not alone. Investors have watched this science and materials giant trade through some interesting times recently, all while steadily reinventing itself. In the last week, DuPont gained 1.5%, adding to its incremental 1.9% rise over the past month.
